      "body": "**Run 0010 T12 reconcile (r8, session 0067-horizon-T12): PASS \u2014 rank-`e` stratum landed + blueprinted.** Session `0067` ran normally (the Fable-5 credit block of the archived `I-0099` is cleared) and delivered a genuine, verified advance.\n\n- **Kernel-verified independently** (Ground): `lake build AlgebraicJacobian.Picard.EntryIdealStratum` green (8584 jobs, exit 0); `#print axioms` on `pointRank`, `strataIdeal`, `map_strataIdeal_basicOpen`, `strataData`, `stratum\u03b9`, `mem_range_stratum\u03b9_iff`, `Ideal.fiberRank_baseChange` each report exactly `[propext, Classical.choice, Quot.sound]` \u2014 no `sorryAx`.\n- **Math soundness** (fresh work-reviewer): no vacuity, no off-by-one, no weaker-than-named statements. Fibre-rank base-change is genuinely flatness-free; strata-ideal quasi-coherence is genuinely noetherian-free; support = rank **exactly** `e`.\n- **New file** `AlgebraicJacobian/Picard/EntryIdealStratum.lean` (806 LOC) builds the canonical rank-`e` stratum as a closed subscheme \u2014 the geometric layer feeding the sole residual `sorry` of the `FlatteningStratification` cone, `flatLocusStratification_universal`.\n- **Blueprint debt cleared**: the `blueprint` subagent added a full section `sec:flatstrat_rank_stratum` (24 `\\lean`-anchored, `\\leanok`, complete-proof nodes) to `Picard_FlatteningStratification.tex`; DAG caches refreshed \u2192 **AJC 0 dangling**.\n\n**Two honest gaps handed back to Horizon (not defects):**\n- The universal theorem prose asserts a **representability/factorization** of morphisms through the stratum that the Lean does not yet provide (only set-theoretic support + the closed subscheme). Its proof correctly stays un-`\\leanok`; closing it is Stage D of the route.\n- `ChartsCover G e` is an explicit hypothesis (it forces fibre rank `\u2264 e` everywhere), **not** derived from noetherian+coherent. Stage D/E must discharge it for the actual base (the `X := W_e` instantiation). No `horizon run` change needed; `AJ